  <!-- EN: Igor Invader -->
  <VFEMech-IgorInvader.label>“入侵者”伊戈尔</VFEMech-IgorInvader.label>
  <!-- EN: Igor Invader holds no regard for boring stories about thriving colonies. The only story worth telling is the one of combat. He will send raids every two or three days, rewarding players for dealing with them swiftly, and punishing player for any losses. This storyteller doubles all damage types, but also warns you about upcoming raids 12 hours before they happen. -->
  <VFEMech-IgorInvader.description>伊戈尔对繁荣昌盛殖民地的无聊故事毫无兴趣。唯一值得讲述的只有战斗的故事。他每两到三天会发动一次突袭，给予快速处理的殖民地以奖励，并对殖民地任何的损失进行惩罚。这个故事叙述者使所有类型的伤害加倍。</VFEMech-IgorInvader.description>
  
